snippet.title: Blockville Official Trailer
snippet.description:
STEAM : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1937200/Blockville/
TWITTER : https://twitter.com/blockvillegame

Blockville is a peaceful stylized city building simulation game where you can relax and build a city inspired by the toys you all used to play with when you were young. Now you have an excuse to play again as an adult in this stylized city sim.
